<li class="leaf menu-mlid-961 tobacco-use depth-5 same-level-as-node"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/nz-health-statistics/national-collections-and-surveys/surveys/past-surveys/tobacco-use-survey">Tobacco use</a></li>
<li class="last leaf menu-mlid-963 other-surveys depth-5 same-level-as-node"><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/nz-health-statistics/national-collections-and-surveys/surveys/past-surveys/other-surveys">Other surveys</a></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></div>
