  <div class="pane-content">
        <div class="view view-related-content-revisioning view-id-related_content_revisioning view-display-id-block_4 view-dom-id-0bbe0a8fd63ce76eae2173719e471c76">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
          
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-text-block-revision-id">        <div class="field-content"><h3>Publications</h3>

<ul>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/drug-use-new-zealand-key-results-2007-08-new-zealand-alcohol-and-drug-use-survey">Drug Use in New Zealand: Key results of the 2007/08 New Zealand Alcohol and Drug Use Survey</a></li>
	<li>Alcohol Use in New Zealand: Key results of the 2007/08 New Zealand Alcohol and Drug Use Survey [<a href="http://www.moh.govt.nz/notebook/nbbooks.nsf/mohwebsearch?readform">refer Library Catalogue</a>]</li>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/methodology-report-2007-08-new-zealand-alcohol-and-drug-use-survey">Methodology Report for the 2007/08 New Zealand Alcohol and Drug Use Survey</a></li>
	<li><a href="https://www.health.govt.nz/publication/2007-08-new-zealand-alcohol-and-drug-use-survey-online-data-tables">Appendix 1: Online data tables of the 2007/08 New Zealand Alcohol and Drug Use Survey</a></li>
	<li>Alcohol Use in New Zealand: Analysis of the 2004 New Zealand Health Behaviours Survey &ndash; Alcohol Use [<a href="http://www.moh.govt.nz/notebook/nbbooks.nsf/mohwebsearch?readform">refer Library Catalogue</a>]</li>
	<li>Drug Use in New Zealand: Analysis of the 2003 New Zealand Health Behaviours Survey &ndash; Drug Use [<a href="http://www.moh.govt.nz/notebook/nbbooks.nsf/mohwebsearch?readform">refer Library Catalogue</a>]</li>
</ul>
</div>  </div>    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
